{"tid":1742631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣警告]各區連儂牆被徹底清洗","createTime":"2019-11-21T01:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T02:05:03.000Z","uid":4568,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8c8e51db80f2a2de0f1243dd3d49ab41a82a2f","tid":1742631,"uid":4568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"啱啱一早出門 發現各區既文宣都被大規模清洗左<br />\n<br />\n睇返tg group 原來啲狗半夜cover啲清潔人員<br />\n<br />\n拎埋高壓水槍清晒<br />\n<br />\n原本一大幅既都一點不漏比人清晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n極有組織 懷疑因為區選在即<br />\n<br />\n召集所以手足 唔理你係和理勇武<br />\n<br />\n都要出黎幫手貼文宣 貼多啲資訊性既野<br />\n<br />\n好似講tg既禍害 以及各區候選人既資料<br />\n<br />\n比啲上左年齡既人睇 唔好再留係同溫層！！<br />\n<br />\n好多老人家或者中年人接收資訊既速度或者方法其實都好慢好少<br />\n<br />\n佢地好多都唔識玩電話 所以文宣就變得非常重要<br />\n<br />\n手足們我地一齊再貼返滿佢呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n比啲圖海大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kz8ouM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kz8ouM.jpg&h=1fa77ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gy5qH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gy5qH7.jpg&h=fb32cf4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVcU3uO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVcU3uO.jpg&h=d9bdd6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRFY29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRFY29.jpg&h=6f5e751a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8quTzBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?