"},{"pid":"dcb873beefd12160ff7408b183c442c6b4139581","tid":1742631,"uid":173889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"而家連儂牆比人清得7788<br />\n個社會開始變番正常番工放工<br />\n港豬好善忘..無文宣提住佢地好快會唔記得<br />\nFB轉發一陣就唔見晒D貼,點都唔夠連儂牆咁聚人心<br />\n而家只有小貓3,4隻自發去貼,跟不停比狗撚<br />\n而家差既係和理非人數<br />\n佢地唔敢出黎行...出黎貼野夠晒安全啦！？<br />\n<br />\n大家請記住 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n前線同和理非而家係話唔割席..但係少左樣野connect埋一齊！<br />\n前線做既野比如黎明有作用,連儂牆都有佢地既作用 就係提醒各位香港人抗爭遠未結束！<br />\n<br />\n而家有國際戰線,,有黎明抗爭,,與其比和理非係度做鍵盤戰士,,不如真真正正搞個活動比佢地幫手重建連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a6c8195981cae76d1122f6aae4374c31dea199","tid":1742631,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=81f078f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f9f95382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e637f76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e5f2d263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"d9c58ea709806a6eafd3d572f94da1d4c844643a","tid":1742631,"uid":600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d8690cce49552093889073dca27b09931eb9867","tid":1742631,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b30a0e01f02e9e887251b965f94270a97d4496b1","tid":1742631,"uid":132283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"大家寧願塞鐵都唔肯做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"咁行動都好重要既，唔係d人真係以為我哋d行動派比人拉灑"},{"pid":"0a5e2478e16d4ac19873efc6794b7bb073c8dc07","tid":1742631,"uid":169801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f8615792dbb77921527c724e26a168e5b674313","tid":1742631,"uid":215773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"火炭A出口俾人貼滿哂藍屍文宣可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"我哋唔支持撕紙，但無話唔支持cover佢同換紙喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8b49d1d74c21a38ae6df82e3ce7e92fe4499b5","tid":1742631,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b79c198438ede22b22ab16d6c41f7456a5d25940","tid":1742631,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"清一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日遲左起身，正好print野<br />\n下晝出街貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s